OL,6,FThe minister was speaking to ITV News
OL,7,Fabout new labour market statistics
OL,8,Fwhich show Britain's unemployment rate
OL,9,Fhas hit a near four-year high - but
OL,10,Fthey also revealed wages are rising
OL,11,Ffaster than inflation.
OL,13,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,14,F(ONS) said the latest official figures
OL,15,Fshowed further signs of a "cooling"
OL,16,Flabour market, with average regular
OL,17,Fearnings growth falling to 5.6% in the
OL,18,Fthree months to March.
