OL,6,FThis is down from 5.9% in the previous
OL,7,Fthree months and the lowest level
OL,8,Fsince the three months to November
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FBut wages still outstripped inflation,
OL,12,Frising by 2.6% higher after taking
OL,13,FConsumer Prices Index inflation into
