OL,6,FResponding, Minister Timms said:
OL,7,F"There's been a slight increase in the
OL,8,Funemployment rate this month compared
OL,9,Fwith last. Wage growth is still very
OL,10,Fpositive and I welcome that. That
OL,11,Freally helps lots of us.
OL,13,F"But we are determined to improve the
